## §0 Terminal goal — AI 17-verb 도서관 (4 그룹 모두 working spec)

hexa-codex 도착지 = **AI 17-verb 도서관 (safety + economics + ops + substrate) 모두 working spec + falsifier preregister + 1+ verb wired eval pipeline .hexa**.

DoD:
1. `safety` 그룹 alignment + interpretability eval pipeline .hexa.
2. `economics` 그룹 training-cost / inference-cost n=6 scaling fit (GPT-4 vs Claude 4.7).
3. `ops` 그룹 deploy + agent-serving 통합 .hexa.
4. `substrate` 그룹 multimodal + cog-arch + causal + RLHF 통합 eval.

## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
```

| Symbol | Value | Role | AI projection |
|--------|-------|------|---------------|
| σ(6)   | 12    | sigma — cardinality bin | 12 capability dimensions (HELM bench bin) |
| τ(6)   | 4     | tau — state quartet | 4 lifecycle phases (pretrain / SFT / RLHF / deploy) |
| φ(6)   | 2     | phi — verdict bit | helpful / harmless |
| J₂     | 24    | Mathieu / Leech | training cost ∝ N^J₂ scaling stratum |

